title: Blazing 5 - Week 7

description:
After a brutal week 6 Colin tries to rebound with his Blazing 5 in week 7. RJ Bell of pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio tells him which games the wise guys in Vegas agree and disagree with. Plus, Colin reveals a 6th bonus pick not included in the Blazing 5 exclusive to this podcast.
